OL,3,C'It was a frightening time': Ex-miners
OL,4,Chaunted by memories of Orgreave
OL,6,FThere is little sign today of the
OL,7,Ftrouble which flared at Orgreave 40
OL,8,Fyears ago.
OL,10,FA housing estate sits on the site of
OL,11,Fthe former South Yorkshire coking
OL,12,Fplant. Peace now largely reigns.
OL,14,FBut, for those who lived through it,
OL,15,Fthe memories abide.
OL,17,F"It was a frightening time," says
OL,18,Fformer miner Kevin Horne. "I try not
OL,19,Fto think about it now."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/13
