OL,3,C'It was a frightening time': Ex-miners
OL,4,Chaunted by memories of Orgreave
OL,6,FKevin was one of thousands of miners
OL,7,Fwho were involved in violent clashes
OL,8,Fwith police, in what became known as
OL,9,Fthe Battle of Orgreave, on 18 June
OL,10,F1984.
OL,12,FThe incident ` three months into the
OL,13,Fminers' strike ` happened after the
OL,14,FNational Union of Mineworkers
OL,15,Forganised a mass picket to prevent
OL,16,Fdeliveries of coal arriving at the
OL,17,Fplant, near Rotherham.
OL,19,FAlmost 5,000 officers in riot gear
OL,20,Fwere sent to police the picket.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/13
