OL,3,C'It was a frightening time': Ex-miners
OL,4,Chaunted by memories of Orgreave
OL,6,FFilmmaker Daniel Gordon has made a
OL,7,Fdocumentary about the events. He said
OL,8,Flooking into the history of the battle
OL,9,Fhad opened his eyes.
OL,11,F"I thought I knew about the strike and
OL,12,FI thought I knew about the effects
OL,13,Fthat it had and I thought I knew about
OL,14,FOrgreave and the more I got into it,
OL,15,Fthe more I realise how little I knew,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/13
