OL,3,C'It was a frightening time': Ex-miners
OL,4,Chaunted by memories of Orgreave
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police has said it
OL,7,Fintends to publish as many documents
OL,8,Frelating to Orgreave as possible
OL,9,Fwithin the next couple of years.JFor
OL,10,Fthe likes of Jane Colbourne and Susan
OL,11,FCairns' that kind of transparency is
OL,12,Flong overdue.
OL,14,FTheir father, miner Tony Arkwright,
OL,15,Fcompiled pictures, cuttings and hand
OL,16,Fwritten notes documenting what
OL,17,Fhappened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/13
