OL,3,C'It was a frightening time': Ex-miners
OL,4,Chaunted by memories of Orgreave
OL,6,FJane said: "This is something that we
OL,7,Fcan sit down with our grandkids and
OL,8,Fsay 'great grandad did that.' This is
OL,9,Fgoing to be history to the kids of the
OL,10,Ffuture. And I think it's important
OL,11,Fthat the true picture, the fair
OL,12,Fpicture of what happened is out
OL,13,Fthere."J"He got photos that the press
OL,14,Fwouldn't show and it's there for
OL,15,Fanybody to see. And I hope there is an
OL,16,Finquiry at some point, because a lot
OL,17,Fof lives were ruined."JFor Kevin Horne
OL,18,Fonly an independent, Hillsborough-
OL,19,Fstyle inquiry into the events at
OL,20,FOrgreave will sufficientlyJ"If they
OL,21,Fcould do that, then everything would
OL,22,Fcome out. That's my dream, like. So
OL,23,Fthat people in the pub, who you've
OL,24,Ftalked to over the years, know that
OL,25,Fyou've been telling the truth."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/13
