OL,3,C'It was a frightening time': Ex-miners
OL,4,Chaunted by memories of Orgreave
OL,6,FLabour's manifesto includes a
OL,7,Fcommitment to an investigation.
OL,9,FThe Liberal Democrats, Green Party and
OL,10,FReform Party all say they are
OL,11,Fsupportive of an inquiry.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, South Yorkshire Police said
OL,14,Fit would be inappropriate for the
OL,15,Fforce to seek to "explain or defend
OL,16,Fthe actions of the force in 1984".
OL,18,FIt said in a statement: "We have been
OL,19,Fvery clear about our intention to make
OL,20,Fas much of the relevant documentation
OL,21,Fas is possible available to the public.
