OL,6,F"To that end, a small team, funded by
OL,7,Fthe then Police and Crime
OL,8,FCommissioner, is reviewing and
OL,9,Fcataloguing all of the material held
OL,10,Fby the force and ensuring anything
OL,11,Freleased is done so in line with the
OL,12,Frequirements of GDPR. There are 1,474
OL,13,Ffiles of material which amount to
OL,14,F82,913 pages.
